<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id8ebcc23e-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6" identifier="/us/usc/t22/s284cc"><num value="284cc">§ 284cc.</num><heading> Nineteenth replenishment</heading><subsection style="-uslm-lc:I19" class="indent2 firstIndent-2" id="id8ebcc23f-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6" identifier="/us/usc/t22/s284cc/a"><num value="a" class="bold">(a)</num><heading class="bold"> In general</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The United States Governor of the International Development Association is authorized to contribute on behalf of the United States $3,004,200,000 to the nineteenth replenishment of the resources of the Association, subject to obtaining the necessary appropriations.</p>
</content>
</subsection>
<subsection style="-uslm-lc:I19" class="indent2 firstIndent-2" id="id8ebcc240-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6" identifier="/us/usc/t22/s284cc/b"><num value="b" class="bold">(b)</num><heading class="bold"> Authorization of appropriations</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">In order to pay for the United States contribution provided for in subsection (a), there are authorized to be appropriated, without fiscal year limitation, $3,004,200,000 for payment by the Secretary of the Treasury.</p>
</content>
</subsection>
<sourceCredit id="id8ebcc241-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6">(<ref href="/us/pl/86/565/s31">Pub. L. 86–565, § 31</ref>, as added <ref href="/us/pl/116/136/dB/tXI/s21012/b/1">Pub. L. 116–136, div. B, title XI, § 21012(b)(1)</ref>, <date date="2020-03-27">Mar. 27, 2020</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/134/593">134 Stat. 593</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
